Skip the grind and get your Path of Exile character power-leveled in record time with our 5 Way Power Leveling service. Whether you're rushing to endgame content or want to save hours of monotonous leveling, our professional carries are the fastest and safest way to level up.
What you'll get:
A set number of 5 Way carry runs;
Access to optimized XP farming groups;
Completely manual service — no bots or macros.

Buy PoE Autumn Knight Armour boost and obtain all rewards from The Legacy of Phrecia event quickly, effortlessly, and guaranteed. This way, you will reach level 80 of your character, unlock all passive points, and, most importantly, get all armor pieces of the limited Autumn Knight set!
Let our PROs do all the hard work for you, and leave the grind behind!
The rewards of The Legacy of Phrecia are:
Level 20 - Autumn Knight Boots;
Level 40 - Autumn Knight Gloves;
Level 60 - Autumn Knight Body Armour;
Level 80 - Autumn Knight Helmet.
With our PoE Autumn Knight Set farming service, you will get:
Character level reached up to the chosen reward;
The unique Autumn Knight Armour set that will be available in both PoE 1 and PoE 2;
3 free labs completed with all passive points unlocked when choosing the entire set (level 80);

